headline.main: Goggia Edges Vonn for Second Day on 2018 Olympic Course
headline.print_headline: Goggia Edges Vonn for Second Day on 2018 Olympic Course

lead_paragraph: Sofia Goggia edged Lindsey Vonn into second place at a World Cup event for the second time in two days, winning the Super-G at the 2018 Olympic course on Sunday to follow her victory in the downhill.
